00:04:08.370 --> 00:04:10.839
Monsters University
In spite of the fact that she was outright

00:04:10.839 --> 00:04:15.620
offered the role of Dean Abigail Hardscrabble
in Monsters University, Helen Mirren requested

00:04:15.620 --> 00:04:20.030
that she audition for it anyway to ensure
that the people behind the movie were satisfied

00:04:20.030 --> 00:04:22.240
with her performance.

